description: It's not mascara, it's false lash glam in a tube, instantly! Patented spoon brush and pro-keratin fiber formula instantly build 5x more volume without clumping. Unique flexible wand helps lift and separate, to provide the look of 2x more lashes. You will find lashes you didn't even know you had. To safeguard Maybelline purity, reserve this product for your personal use. Treat the applicator with the hygienic care you give your eyes. Never apply this product in a moving vehicle.
